title: 2 FLOOR TOWNHOUSE * PRIVATE BACKYARD * IN UNIT WASHER DRYER * 2 BATHS
posting_body: ['2 Floor house plus finished basement, in unit washer dryer and private backyard!', 'Located in the heart of Bedford-Stuyvesant, Brooklyn.', 'This newly gut renovated triplex apartment was designed with modern sophistication.', 'The Apartment Boasts 4 Bedrooms, 2 Full Baths, and 2 Half Baths.', 'This Triplex allows the use of three levels including a Finished Tiled Basement.', 'The key-less entry walks you straight into an Open Layout living room and kitchen.', 'This open floor concept provides a simplistic elegance for your creativity.', 'Journeying upstairs we find a spacious Master Bedroom with a huge double door closet.', 'The Italian tiled master bathroom includes a double sink ensuite with a luxurious waterfall overhead shower panel.', 'Down the hall you will find two beautiful bedrooms with high ceilings.', 'Enjoy a stunning electric fireplace with a state of the art washer and dryer in unit.', 'The basement can also be used as an additional bedroom.', 'The sliding doors from the kitchen leads to a Private backyard perfect for entertaining.', 'Enjoy a blend of restaurants, bars, and cafes within the diverse community.', 'Buses B15, B38, and B54 are nearby, along with access to the J, M, G, A, C trains located within proximity.', 'Text Leo: 917-808-0442']
